text:
Decent place for a drink.  I wouldn't sit long though as it's pretty humid. No air circulators outside.

Service was decent.
Service is very quick, staff is welcoming! Food was good and the atmosphere is good in vibrant street. I like the experience for a quick bite
Pizza from madd pizza can be ordered here and will be delivered to your table. Craft beers taste good but drinking in Singapore is expensive.

Another great happy hour on Haji Ln and a perfect intersection for some great people watching. Lots of seating inside and out with the bar extending onto the adjoining lane. We enjoyed some tiger and house wine while watching the lane unfoldüëåüèª
